## ğŸ”§ Configuration

Create `.athena/config.yaml`:

```yaml
memory:
  qdrant_url: "http://localhost:6333"
  collection_name: "athena_memories"
  
evolution:
  auto_track: true
  rule_threshold: 2
  
personalization:
  enable_mkm12: true
  learning_rate: 0.1
```

